# Prefer `var` for Local Variables

Use `var` for local variable declarations when the inferred type is clear.

```java
// ✅ preferred
var request = new GenerateRequest();
var response = speechWorkerService.generate(request);

// ❌ avoid
GenerateRequest request = new GenerateRequest();
GenerateResponse response = speechWorkerService.generate(request);
```
